'''Pho̍k''' (雹) ya ham cho '''pên-pho̍k''' (冰雹), he thiên sông tiet lo̍k lòi ke [[pên]], chhṳ̍t-kang yû 5 to 150 [[hò-mí]]. Thai-yok pho̍k thûng-siòng he kín-sùi tá-[[Lùi-kûng|lùi]] [[ngiap-lang]] lòi ke, voi khon to [[chit-yí-yùn]]. Liá ko-chhàng chhiu he '''lo̍k-pho̍k''' (落雹).

